beer.beer_description:
This is our foundation beer. Amber ales were an epiphany style for us back in the 90's when we could only find bland fizzy lagers. We still love their complexity.

We've been brewing this classic English-style amber ale since 1997 which makes it one of Melbourne's earliest craft beers.

Appearance: Deep copper/amber colour. Slightly beige head.
Aroma: Subtle fruitiness, which makes way for toffee-like crystal malt notes. 
Flavour: Toffee and nut flavours, palate is clean and dry.

Malts: Ale, Munich, Wheat, Crystal and Roast. 
Hops: Cascade and Galaxy.
